caption:
Global Pet Expo was a blast! It was great to catch up with many old, familiar faces as well as meet so many new people. 

In an industry we’re so deeply rooted in, it’s exciting to see new, innovative brands, shaking things up and having the ability to compete with the giant conglomerates that dominate this market.

The future is bright!💡
